ever...but it is something they have never gotten before that we always had. </P><P>Im not jealous of what the other classes got, Im glad for them. But I think we got screwed over on ours getting a level 49 spell rehash with a longer casting time. Even if it is free damage...thats 9 seconds that I gotta stand there and wait for it to go off. 9 seconds into the battle the thing could be nearly dead, or totally resist it. Now Ive lost 9 seconds that I could have used to cast 2 or 3 other spells.</P><P>As far as a useful effect, sure...it may be useful in certian situations...but I dont think it belongs on what is supposed to be the pinnacle of Necro achievement.</P><P> </font></td>
