el 60 necro operating at his MAXIMUM efficiency can SOLO:</P><P>Golden Efreeti(doable by shaman, mage w/epic, enchanter, druid maybe)<BR>Alliwezaur(doable by shaman, mage, enchanter who is bored, druid)<BR>Old Wurms(doable by shaman, mage w/epic, enchanter, druid, wizard)<BR>Ancient Wyverns that doesn't summon(doable by shaman, chanter w/risk, wizard, druid)<BR>Priest of Discord(nobody else ever tried so I don't know, maybe he is particular to necros)<BR>Chardok mobs that don't summon(doable by shamans, chanters, mages, druids)<BR>Sebilis mobs that don't summon(doable by shamans, chanters, mages, druids, monks)<BR>HS mobs that don't summon(doable by shamans, chanters, druids)<BR>What else???</P><P></P><P>Etadanik the Redeemed</font></td>
